name: Tree of Life and Death
description: Life and Death are one thread, the same line viewed from different sides  They coexist in an endless cycle. Endings are not always bad: Life can flourish again, feeding on the dead. There cannot be life without death, it is inescapable.  On a man's grave stands a tree, ready to welcome its history and reabsorb its essence back to nothing. And no one can escape from this destiny. This NFT is used on NFT Pixel Project and 11% of all proceeds will be given to #Walk2EndALZ (Alzheimer’s) charity. More infos are available here: http://nftpixelproject.com/.
